#pagination.panel
	.panel-header
		h3.panel-title Pagination
	.panel-body
		P A pagination component. Style sheets linking occurs when the #[code .pagination] primary class is present on the page.
		p Component example:
		nav( aria-label='Page navigation example' )
			ul.pagination.mt-1
				li.page-item
					a.page-link( href='#' ) Previous
				li.page-item
					a.page-link( href='#' ) 1
				li.page-item
					a.page-link( href='#' ) 2
				li.page-item
					a.page-link( href='#' ) 3
				li.page-item
					a.page-link( href='#' ) Next

		p Code example:
		pre.highlight.html
			= '<nav aria-label="Page navigation example">\n'
			= '  <ul class="pagination">\n'
			= '    <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">Previous</a></li>\n'
			= '    <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">1</a></li>\n'
			= '    <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">2</a></li>\n'
			= '    <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">3</a></li>\n'
			= '    <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">Next</a></li>\n'
			= '  </ul>\n'
			= '</nav>'

		p This component is a part of #[a( href='https://getbootstrap.com' ) Bootstrap 4] framework. Read more about it on the following page: #[a( href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/components/pagination" ) Bootstrap Pagination].
